'''達里奧·大衛·亨特'''（{{lang-en|Dario David Hunter}}；{{bd|1983年|4月21日}}<ref name="about-dario">{{cite web |title=About Dario |url=https://www.dariohunter.com/about_dario |website=Hunter 2020 |accessdate=January 29, 2019 |archive-date=2020-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127173124/https://www.dariohunter.com/about_dario |dead-url=no }}</ref>），又名'''伊斯洛爾·亨特'''（{{lang|en|Yisroel Hunter}}）<ref name="about-dario" />，是美國一名[[拉比|拉比]]、律師和政治人物，也是第一位獲授與拉比的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]男性<ref name="ynet">{{cite web|title=NYC: Ex-Muslim to be ordained as rabbi|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4251324,00.html|work=YNetNews.com|date=July 7, 2012|accessdate=August 26, 2012|archive-date=2012-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120709235823/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4251324,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tablet">{{cite web|title=Black Jews You Should Know, Part 4|url=http://www.tabletmag.com/scroll/197992/blackjew-you-should-know-4|work=Tablet Magazine|date=February 25, 2016|accessdate=June 28, 2016|archive-date=2016-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160227113841/http://www.tabletmag.com/scroll/197992/blackjew-you-should-know-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他曾擔任[[揚斯敦_(俄亥俄州)|俄亥俄州揚斯敦]]教育局成員，並曾尋求[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年]][[2020年美國總統選舉綠黨初選|綠黨初選]]總統提名，最終排在第二。隨後他得到{{le|俄勒岡州進步黨|Oregon Progressive Party}}的提名，並於其他州份用進步黨的名義出選美國總統選舉<ref name="CPD">{{cite web |last1=Pelzer |first1=Jeremy |title=Youngstown School Board member Dario Hunter seeks Green Party presidential nomination |url=https://www.cleveland.com/politics/2019/02/youngstown-school-board-member-dario-hunter-seeks-green-party-presidential-nomination.html |website=Cleveland.com |accessdate=March 4, 2019 |date=February 19, 2019 |archive-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190219211916/https://www.cleveland.com/politics/2019/02/youngstown-school-board-member-dario-hunter-seeks-green-party-presidential-nomination.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BAN1">{{Cite web|url=https://ballot-access.org/2020/08/25/progressive-party-of-oregon-nominates-dario-hunter-for-president/|work=Ballot Access News|date=Aug 25, 2020|accessdate=Aug 26, 2020|title=Progressive Party of Oregon Nominates Dario Hunter for President|archive-date=2020-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826032603/https://ballot-access.org/2020/08/25/progressive-party-of-oregon-nominates-dario-hunter-for-president/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Denver">{{cite web |last1=Murray |first1=Jon |title=Presidential candidates on Colorado’s November 2029 ballot |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2020/08/19/presidential-candidates-2020-colorado-ballot/ |website=The Denver Post |accessdate=Aug 24, 2020 |date=Aug 19, 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913074627/https://www.denverpost.com/2020/08/19/presidential-candidates-2020-colorado-ballot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==背景==
亨特是一名[[同性戀|同性戀]]者，由他的[[伊朗|伊朗]]穆斯林父親和非裔美國人母親在[[紐華克_(紐澤西州)|紐華克]]和[[泽西市|泽西市]]撫養長大<ref name="arabiya">{{cite web |title=Muslim-born American to be ordained as rabbi in New York |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/07/07/225074.html |work=Al-Arabiya News |date=July 7, 2012 |accessdate=August 26, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829212523/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/07/07/225074.html |archive-date=August 29, 2012 }}</ref>。

他曾在以色列擔任環境律師，其後在俄亥俄州[[扬斯敦_(俄亥俄州)|揚斯敦]]擔任公會拉比，及在[[伍斯特学院|伍斯特学院]]擔任校園拉比，目前居住在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]<ref name="CPD"/><ref name="arabiya"/><ref name="about-dario"/><ref name="votedario">{{cite web|title=Dario Hunter for Youngstown City Council, Ward 6|url=http://votedario.com|accessdate=January 13, 2015|website=votedario.com|archive-date=2015-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212033508/http://votedario.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

